{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDg4Mjc4NDYz", "number": 7813, "title": "allow for line-by-line execution of Python chunks", "bodyText": "Intent\nCurrently, Python chunks can only be executed a whole chunk at a time. We should bring the execution of Python chunks into parity with R chunks, which can be executed line-by-line or with specific selections.\nApproach\nUse the existing Notebook execution machinery for code execution, but modify the executed code to ensure that the reticulate Python REPL is activated / deactivated as appropriate.\nQA Notes\nCreate an R Markdown document, with both R and Python chunks. Try to write and execute code within those chunks. Confirm that:\n\nPython chunks can be executed line-by-line, or by selecting a region and executing that region;\nExecuting R code, then Python code, causes RStudio to automatically switch to the reticulate REPL (you should see reticulate::repl_python() executed in the console).\n\n\nCloses #6256.", "createdAt": "2020-09-16T22:29:23Z", "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/pull/7813", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "fb9528de7cf8eb24b1a5da2f67ecf5d6dccc3c2e"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-09-28T17:45:32Z", "author": {"login": "kevinushey"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 6, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdJkFy8AH2gAyNDg4Mjc4NDYzOjgxMTRjYTQ5YjA5NmI2Mjk4ODQwYTZkYmYxMDgxYmQxYTdkMjg5ODM=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdNXQ_3AH2gAyNDg4Mjc4NDYzOmJhYjU3YjExMmU2N2U4YTI1YTNmMTBjY2U4OGIyNDc2NjdhZmZhNzY=", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "8114ca49b096b6298840a6dbf1081bd1a7d28983", "author": {"user": {"login": "kevinushey", "name": "Kevin Ushey"}}, "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/commit/8114ca49b096b6298840a6dbf1081bd1a7d28983", "committedDate": "2020-09-16T22:25:28Z", "message": "allow for line-by-line execution of Python chunks"}}, {"__typename": "PullR